title: Ex Midtjylland Striker Jude Nworuh Joins Bnei Yehuda
text:
15:55 CET Ex Midtjylland Striker Jude Nworuh Joins Bnei Yehuda - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Former FC Midtjylland striker Jude Nworuh has ended speculation about his future by penning a contract with Bnei Yehuda, following a successful trial that lasted for about a week. 
The FC Ebedei product has appended his signature to a two â€“ year contract that will keep him at The Lions until June 30, 2017.
